16 4. As used in this section:
17 (a) “Sanctioned sport” means any athletic competition that is
18 approved by the Nevada Interscholastic Activities Association.
19 (b) “Wrap-around services” means support services provided to
20 pupils who participate in a sanctioned sport, including, without
21 limitation, tutoring or other supplemental academic achievement
22 programs, college and career counseling and mentoring.
23 Sec. 5. The Nevada Interscholastic Activities Association shall
